snippet.title: The Life of a Magical Circle - Free Re-release Trailer
snippet.description:
The Life of a Magical Circle is a roguelite in which you dodge obstacles and pick up circles. It's a game about finding your purpose in life and focusing on it, and you'll have to figure it all out with only a little help from your mysterious narrator.

Now available for free!

https://store.steampowered.com/app/2408890/The_Life_of_a_Magical_Circle/
